{"componentChunkName":"component---src-pages-posts-asciidoc-page-attributes-slug-tsx","path":"/posts/linux-rhythmbox-osdlyrics/","result":{"data":{"asciidoc":{"id":"2de1a7f9-1e83-570c-8867-2af21bed07a5","html":"<div id=\"preamble\">\n<div class=\"sectionbody\">\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>Ubuntu 22.04 使用 Rhythmbox 播放音乐，OSDLyrics 显示歌词。</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sect1\">\n<h2 id=\"_安装_osdlyrics\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#_安装_osdlyrics\"></a>安装 osdlyrics</h2>\n<div class=\"sectionbody\">\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-bash\" data-lang=\"bash\">sudo apt install osdlyrics</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>从终端启动 osdlyrics 如果出现如下错误：</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-txt\" data-lang=\"txt\">Gtk-Message: 09:28:16.768: Failed to load module \"canberra-gtk-module\"\n*Error*: in function _start_daemon_cb: ol_main.c[769]\nUnable to start daemon: GDBus.Error:org.freedesktop.DBus.Error.Spawn.ChildExited: Process org.osdlyrics.Daemon exited with status 1</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>安装缺失的依赖：</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-bash\" data-lang=\"bash\">sudo apt install python3-pycurl\nsudo apt install python3-future</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>osdlyrics 可以根据标题和艺人自动搜索歌词。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"imageblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<img src=\"/images/linux-rhythmbox-osdlyrics.png\" alt=\"linux rhythmbox osdlyrics\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sect1\">\n<h2 id=\"_参考\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#_参考\"></a>参考</h2>\n<div class=\"sectionbody\">\n<div class=\"ulist\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/osdlyrics/osdlyrics/issues/75\" class=\"bare\">https://github.com/osdlyrics/osdlyrics/issues/75</a></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>","document":{"title":"Linux Rhythmbox OSDLyrics"},"pageAttributes":{"slug":"linux-rhythmbox-osdlyrics","category":"linux"},"revision":{"date":"2022-08-21","number":"1.0"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"2de1a7f9-1e83-570c-8867-2af21bed07a5","pageAttributes__slug":"linux-rhythmbox-osdlyrics","__params":{"pageAttributes__slug":"linux-rhythmbox-osdlyrics"}}},"staticQueryHashes":["3143286284"],"slicesMap":{}}